<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">
I think Mythic handled it correctly.  It's important to respond promptly and clearly when someone posts like that reposter did.  That guy IS an asshole, particularly when he so rudely (and inaccurately) criticized Camelot.  <P>Since the game is still being developed, it's very important for the beta testers to be willing and able to comment freely.  That will help the game during the development cycle.  Beta testing comments are for internal use by the development team and shouldn't be posted out on public boards like that reposter did.  <P>Kudos to the beta testers for helping to debug Camelot before it gets to me.  Kudos to Mythic for responding to that asshole reposter.  Thanks to everyone for putting in a lot of time in the development and debugging of Camelot.  Keep up the good work.<P>-Turcott-
